{"tid":586822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"舒淇自爆被母親嫌棄：怎麼會有人長得像你那麼醜","createTime":"2018-03-10T01:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T17:28:24.000Z","uid":22349,"like":430,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"80f112db0bd83a206fed1076ec944da27b10a1a0","tid":586822,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"影后舒淇早前因皮膚敏感短暫「息影」，雖然已放風表示將於暑假回歸，但不少粉絲仍望她早日歸隊。近日有內地媒體就公開舒淇的訪問，對於擁有完美身段，每次踏上紅地氈亦成為焦點，舒淇則自爆小時候並非那麼突出，頭髮是自然曲，五官亦不是標準的美女模樣，故曾被母親嫌棄，她謂：「我媽媽說我長得特別醜，怎麼會有人長得像你那麼醜，但是就是因為受到母親長期吐槽，當我面對其他人對我的外貌指點時，我也沒有太大的感覺了。」"},{"pid":"434fc6471ae1916c13af699cf9b0569c631f0708","tid":586822,"uid":22349,"like":58,"dislike":7,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180310/photo/bkn-20180310051548588-0310_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180310073115\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180310%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180310051548588-0310_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180310073115&h=18b200c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9e127dbe376a91f7b1568576efb657e6a8f8a93","tid":586822,"uid":119594,"like":1700,"dislike":49,"score":1651,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"而家咪都係樣衰,有乜分別"},{"pid":"a9e67e1b584ce94f40e4fbbc78208fc707fb5bee","tid":586822,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9e127dbe376a91f7b1568576efb657e6a8f8a93","tid":586822,"uid":119594,"like":1700,"dislike":49,"score":1651,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"而家咪都係樣衰,有乜分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6526cc4ad153b4628445e7f6ca9ec28489ac3a","tid":586822,"uid":4135,"like":174,"dislike":24,"score":150,"quote":{"pid":"434fc6471ae1916c13af699cf9b0569c631f0708","ti